  "detailed_description": "Betrayer: Curse of the Spine is a side-scrolling Action Adventure game that places an emphasis on player decisions. Featuring intricate story telling, a vast world to explore, valuable crafting, and multiple endings to experience. This highly atmospheric game is filled with drama, mystery, and dread.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crafting at the Core</h2><br>Part of overcoming the challenges in this world is learning to use all the tools you have at your disposal. One of the most valuable pieces of your toolkit is your ability to craft. Make potions to restore your health or to increase your strength. Make weapons to brutalize your enemies and armor to protect your tender bits. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/11491713991ed4b409aa18bda306e24f.poster.avif?t=1668477648\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/11491713991ed4b409aa18bda306e24f.webm?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/11491713991ed4b409aa18bda306e24f.mp4?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deadly Platforming and Skilled Combat</h2><br>Not only will your wits be put to the test but your reflexes will as well. It's not all just stabby-stab. Run and jump your way to victory - and likely die trying, many times, before you succeed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/50ea2e7b0d299dfa7d4b12ceeaecbf92.poster.avif?t=1668477648\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/50ea2e7b0d299dfa7d4b12ceeaecbf92.webm?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/50ea2e7b0d299dfa7d4b12ceeaecbf92.mp4?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reveal the World of the Betrayer</h2><br>A land shrouded in darkness and mystery. Unlock the secrets of an ancient world and learn who you really are. Have we been here before? Multiple endings create high replayability.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/5064ef78ba6fd6247cc48f0c86c2bf1b.poster.avif?t=1668477648\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/5064ef78ba6fd6247cc48f0c86c2bf1b.webm?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/5064ef78ba6fd6247cc48f0c86c2bf1b.mp4?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Come Heckle Us</h2><br>",
  "about_the_game": "Betrayer: Curse of the Spine is a side-scrolling Action Adventure game that places an emphasis on player decisions. Featuring intricate story telling, a vast world to explore, valuable crafting, and multiple endings to experience. This highly atmospheric game is filled with drama, mystery, and dread.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Crafting at the Core</h2><br>Part of overcoming the challenges in this world is learning to use all the tools you have at your disposal. One of the most valuable pieces of your toolkit is your ability to craft. Make potions to restore your health or to increase your strength. Make weapons to brutalize your enemies and armor to protect your tender bits. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/11491713991ed4b409aa18bda306e24f.poster.avif?t=1668477648\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/11491713991ed4b409aa18bda306e24f.webm?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/11491713991ed4b409aa18bda306e24f.mp4?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deadly Platforming and Skilled Combat</h2><br>Not only will your wits be put to the test but your reflexes will as well. It's not all just stabby-stab. Run and jump your way to victory - and likely die trying, many times, before you succeed.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/50ea2e7b0d299dfa7d4b12ceeaecbf92.poster.avif?t=1668477648\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/50ea2e7b0d299dfa7d4b12ceeaecbf92.webm?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/50ea2e7b0d299dfa7d4b12ceeaecbf92.mp4?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reveal the World of the Betrayer</h2><br>A land shrouded in darkness and mystery. Unlock the secrets of an ancient world and learn who you really are. Have we been here before? Multiple endings create high replayability.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/5064ef78ba6fd6247cc48f0c86c2bf1b.poster.avif?t=1668477648\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/5064ef78ba6fd6247cc48f0c86c2bf1b.webm?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382290/extras/5064ef78ba6fd6247cc48f0c86c2bf1b.mp4?t=1668477648\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Come Heckle Us</h2><br>",
